{"tid":158220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"fresh grad IT友唔好作賤自己 開價企硬20k","createTime":"2017-03-16T06:31:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T10:04:24.000Z","uid":19552,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6c209a85053f8c26125b3343387f4f0c5399bb55","tid":158220,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:31:42.000Z","msg":"我細佬今年poly畢業 佢只係一個second low既毒撚 <br />\n但佢係FDM收緊35k <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n相反 佢幾個拎first hon既朋友 5月未出hon就on99草草搵工 <br />\n只係去D濕鳩公司仔收緊15~18k <br />\n<br />\n我投身左IT界幾年 所以大概知道個環境 <br />\n我敢打包單 只要你識coding而你又肯做programmer <br />\n你絕對有資格開20k 以下我同你分析下 <br />\n<br />\n首性從供需角度睇, 香港programmer有咩問題? <br />\n1. 工作環境差 <br />\n2. 不受重視, 不受尊重 <br />\n3. 工時長 <br />\n<br />\n可以講 programmer係一份極度不享受既工作黎! <br />\n肯做programmer而又有能力做programmer既人根本唔多 <br />\n只係做得既都係毒撚成日比老細大起 其實就年年都請唔夠人 <br />\n請到都大機會係開個function都唔識 乜鳩都成段copy黎copy去既垃圾黎 <br />\n<br />\n其次 programmer最大問題就缺少晉升機會 <br />\n大部分司programming team基本上係獨立出黎 <br />\n而programming 本身係一樣非常specific既技能 <br />\n你一走出programming世界 <br />\n你全部既技能知識都係垃圾 <br />\n所以你無得好似其他工跳過去隔離組lead <br />\n你只能等你1001個老頂走人 再鬥贏百鳩幾個同事上位 <br />\n<br />\n你要加人工 只能跳槽 所以你起薪點係極大程度影響你之後既人工! <br />\n<br />\n好多毒撚6月hon都未出就驚到拉屎 周圍鳩衝搵垃圾工 <br />\n但我可以同你講 你肯做programmer 係一定唔洗驚無工做 <br />\n因為programmer係一份垃鳩圾無人肯做既工黎 <br />\n<br />\n你肯做programmer 而又有能力做programmer 你係絕對有資格叫價20k <br />\n到呢家都未搵到工既同學仔 唔洗驚 <br />\n首先你可以比信去FDM試下 就算唔得都唔洗驚 <br />\n搵工潮到9月 公司請programmer人工只會越出越高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09c6935b237bf1b9e923895f38930d14418c97d4","tid":158220,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:35:00.000Z","msg":"IT聽講今年fg ive仔有38K"},{"pid":"53794e0e61782b486f4db9c1737e9e5f35efec75","tid":158220,"uid":46595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:35:18.000Z","msg":"有幾多咁既位開出黎？<br />\n寧願繼續等機會都唔騎牛搵馬嗎？"},{"pid":"6e37122ef1aaa4cdf1544100ad197b5e23311a77","tid":158220,"uid":14716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:36:08.000Z","msg":"Programmer 無得升？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23631050153ec2b9d1300fbac14675949fc36a13","tid":158220,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:39:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Programmer 無得升？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsenior programmer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cd2efbd2e7a176a02a545c9bbcef060f10090f1","tid":158220,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:42:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有幾多咁既位開出黎？<br />\n寧願繼續等機會都唔騎牛搵馬嗎？</blockquote><br />\n一開始比人出低左人工就無得返轉頭<br />\n<br />\n一開始企硬係最好<br />\n<br />\n最少32K"},{"pid":"499caad88b90b90dbf82d154543ab2231ae2c05e","tid":158220,"uid":80212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:44:57.000Z","msg":"佢喺FDM做programmer? 可唔可以問下你細老喺FDM開頭training 係咪無pay？同埋唔做programmer會唔會低啲？會低幾多？"},{"pid":"34b5ea18cc01baacfe95cb20e1a30bc0a702cf55","tid":158220,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:47:08.000Z","msg":"Strong hold <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eba7da706f27c6bf35a8822e961517a122546b6","tid":158220,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:49:01.000Z","msg":"yes,有間出萬九我都唔屌"},{"pid":"0cdc6ad6777f06ed3b0a5c26c2f1218244601865","tid":158220,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T07:00:20.000Z","msg":"總之唔好聽腦魔果D講"},{"pid":"bcaace2aea8a97d8d9153ed07b9f6ec656c80bd3","tid":158220,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T07:06:06.000Z","msg":"我上年i大grad都35k 今年已經43k😁"},{"pid":"